{"tid":672662,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"回復20年前磅數　溫碧霞戰衣要有海潮Feel","createTime":"2018-05-21T07:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T19:26:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0355641d81917bc7bdd93097cf03908e5d1600c8","tid":672662,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"藝人溫碧霞（Irene）為6月舉行的麥花臣演唱會開記者會，穿露背短裙現身的她獲大會送上鮮花，又請工作人員送上海報及演唱會門券給答中題目的現場觀眾。受訪時，Irene透露已揀好歌曲，打算翻唱自己欣賞的歌手的歌曲，包括陳百強等：「最近積極練歌同Keep Fit，練氣好緊要。依家Keep番20年前嘅磅數，102磅，可以着翻以前啲牛仔褲。」<br />\n<br />\n戰衣要華麗同靚<br />\nIrene表示舞台會以花和海為主題。問到會否穿泳裝？她說不會：「一定要華麗同靚，有海潮嘅感覺，飄逸、有美感同型格，有幾個唔同形象。（老公會唔會唔畀你太性感？）唔會，性感係一種美感，自己都好鍾意睇人性感，性感係女人散發出嚟嘅味道，唔知點解永遠都同我扯唔開！我都比較鍾意呢種感覺。」<br />\n<br />\n繼續唔講嘉賓<br />\n說到跳舞，Irene指推了所有工作來練習，希望為粉絲做個難忘和靚的演唱會，留個美好回憶。至於可有壓力？她說：「又唔會，幾輕鬆，最主要係歌比較多，唱20首。我之前都係同一班人一齊唱，所以今次一定要做好多準備，好耐冇試過好似以前咁又唱歌又跳舞，幾享受。」至於嘉賓方面，她繼續保持神秘，只肯說與兩位都合作過：「大家都好鍾意嘅。（歌手？）又係演員又係歌手。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180521052156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180521052156&h=77179dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_02p.jpg?20180521052156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20180521052156&h=2f0934ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_03p.jpg?20180521052156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20180521052156&h=ae2c51cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_04p.jpg?20180521052156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20180521052156&h=9f3466ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_05p.jpg?20180521052156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20180521052156&h=1e11039d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/photo/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_06p.jpg?20180521052156\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20180521052156&h=460faab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180520%2Fbkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001.html&d=JedxukupOXq29ZbJdMFYBDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=226da363\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180520/bkn-20180520171527747-0520_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe1f87cd57ac52823565e0a4076ff4d090240852","tid":672662,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"回眸一笑步生花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405903b69ab3e494adee35e45d8ee451f82ff3cd","tid":672662,"uid":12633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"暴君　率眾妖害人"},{"pid":"a73ef0d7062a0017130f9fb947a1f93789634697","tid":672662,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re